   Source: https://github.com/nf-osi/nf-metadata-dictionary
   Terms:  The collection of metadata terms is made available by NF-OSI under
           a CC0 1.0 public-domain dedication. Individual terms and their
           definitions may be subject to other permissive licenses; consult
           the source for each term.

2. HTAN2 data model (JSON Schemas, v1.1.0)
   Source: https://github.com/ncihtan/htan2-data-model
   Terms:  The upstream repository does not currently declare an explicit
           license. These schemas are public artifacts of the Human Tumor
           Atlas Network (HTAN), an NCI-funded program. They are redistributed
           here for benchmark reproducibility only, with attribution to HTAN.
           No ownership is claimed. This snapshot will be removed or replaced
           on request of the upstream maintainers.

For any use beyond reproducing this benchmark, obtain the schemas from their
upstream sources and observe the upstream terms.
